institutions which it establishes, present all of us with an
opportunity to take charge of our own destiny.
</P>
<P>
"I am confident that if we apply ourselves boldly with
imagination and honesty and embrace the need for fundamental
change we can chart a course for a new future for all the people
of this island," he said.  
