Fu said he appreciates the stance adopted by the Djibouti
government on "one China," and briefed the guests on the Chinese
military.
</P>
<P>
Fathi expressed gratitude for the support and help provided by
China and said he hopes the government and army of Djibouti will
further strengthen the friendly cooperation between the two
countries and armies.
</P>
<P>
Qian Shugen, deputy chief of the general staff of the PLA of
China, was also present during the meeting.
</P>
<P>
The Djibouti guests are here at the invitation of Fu Quanyou.
